Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:33.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91446,93573}Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:35.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:94616,95825}Take my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106127,107420}Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:49.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107420,109088}Hey, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:51.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110715,111758}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114761,117889}Look at her, all battered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117889,120600}I don't know how she can still walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:03.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120600,123227}She must've come here\Nby sheer willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123227,125021}Mom, is Lassie gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125855,127023}She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127023,129734}She traveled\Nall the way from Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129734,131027}It's o wonder she's tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:13.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131027,133029}She just needs plenty of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:14.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133655,134822}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136783,139702}Lassie sacrificed herself\Nfor our mine… For all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:20.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139702,140745}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146042,147585}Grandfather…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:31.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147585,151047}Anyway, we need to take\NLassie to John's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151047,152090}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155551,156678}Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158096,160431}Can you carry Lassie\Nto our home, Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175697,177615}Here. This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184372,186791}Sleep well, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187625,189752}You don't have to go\Nanywhere now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189752,192088}So just relax and take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199011,200430}She's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:21.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200430,201139}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201139,203599}Once she sleeps it off,\Nshe'll be back to normal in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204892,207186}All right, it's time for us to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:30.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207186,210231}But can you imagine\Nshe had to travel 600 miles on foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210231,211983}No wonder she looks so ragged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:36.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211983,216571}That dog had such a marvelous coat,\Nand the travel completely destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216863,218156}Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218156,220616}Grandfather!\NDo you still want to take Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220616,221743}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:46.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221743,226289}I was thinking that a dog\Ncannot be measured by its fur alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226289,229125}It is a truly extraordinary dog,\Nin more than one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230001,231252}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231669,233629}– We'll be going, too.\N– Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233629,235256}You too. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242513,243890}She's fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243890,245475}Are you happy, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245475,246726}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:11.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246726,251731}She's so exhausted that\Nshe may not walk for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251731,253900}You'll need to take\Na good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253900,254567}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256861,259238}So chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280885,283054}John! Breakfast is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283054,284764}I'm changing right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287934,289977}He was sleeping\Non the kitchen floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290895,293648}Good morning.\NHave you slept well, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293648,294732}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295608,297109}Lassie, it's your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297777,299612}You need to get back in shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:03.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299612,303491}You can't eat too heavy food yet,\Nso I made you a soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303491,305493}Let me feed you, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314585,315628}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315628,316504}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316504,317421}Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317421,318631}She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318631,320424}She just fell asleep again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:23.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320424,323761}She feels at ease\Nwhen she rests on your lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335523,337149}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337149,338734}How is Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:39.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339235,339986}All good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339986,342071}She's not ready yet\Nto go for a walk,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342071,344323}but she's slowly recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344323,347493}But her left ear is still all ragged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348411,349662}It's like a battle wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349662,352331}Yes. Maybe that's\Nfor the best, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:57.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352331,357420}That way that old man, Duke Radling,\Nwon't be trying to get his hands on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357420,358170}Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358170,360590}It doesn't matter\Nwhat she looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360590,362300}She's my Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363426,365511}All right, girl, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365511,367388}Hold on a little longer, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371142,373269}You're gonna be fine, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:16.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373269,376188}Very soon we'll be able\Nto run in the field again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377815,379275}I'm going to sleep.\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379734,381444}Okay. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:41.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401005,401881}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402465,403966}You can walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409513,410890}Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:54.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410890,414310}She can finally eat as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417271,418230}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418230,419732}Duke Radling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419732,421025}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:04.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421567,424195}Are you Duke Radling, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424195,426989}We'd like to hear how your mine,\Nfate of which was already sealed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:09.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426989,429909}miraculously managed\Nto restart its operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429909,433663}Unfortunately,\Nit wasn't my achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:14.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433955,434789}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434789,435665}In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436040,437500}Whose was it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:21.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437500,441462}It could be said that I was outwitted\Nby a certain boy and a certain dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:26.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441462,446092}No, certain dog doesn't cut it.\NIt was a first class Rough Collie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:31.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448177,451138}I have a suspicion that it is\Na very interesting story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451138,453891}Do you think\Nyou could tell it to us, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:37.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453891,457019}No. You're journalists, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457019,460648}Yes. We're with the\NLondon Evening News.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:45.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460648,465403}If the mine really owes its\Nwonderful revival to a single person,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465403,468698}I think the world\Ndeserves to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468698,469657}Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469657,472618}Perhaps you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:58.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472618,478457}They both did something really incredible,\Nworth of being admired by many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481711,484880}Invited by the melody\Nof the music you play,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:10.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484880,490011}I started sailing beyond the endless sky,\Nwith a lone pale star as my guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:14.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490011,494015}Like a sail in the wind, I throw out\Nmy chest with pride and push on bravely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494015,497226}Ah, my heart trembles\Nfrom loneliness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:26.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503399,506110}This is all for today's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506110,508863}Make sure you don't forget\Nto do your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518372,519290}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:49.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525129,529300}You walked all this distance\Njust to pick me up? Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531177,532261}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536140,537641}Nice, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:01.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537641,541020}So that's how she comes every day\Nat three o'clock to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541020,542229}John Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542229,544023}That's me. Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:08.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544023,548486}I just heard about Lassie's story\Nfrom Duke Radling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548486,550529}It's a remarkable tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550529,551113}A tale?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551113,553074}Hey. Can you look here\Nfor a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555701,557286}Smile for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557286,558579}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:22.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559163,562583}By a tale I meant\Na wonderful, touching story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563000,567588}"The boy who reopened the mine\Nand his dog's fantastic journey".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:31.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567588,571092}We'd like to cover your story\Nin our newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571092,573094}The Duke himself\Nasked us to publish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573552,575221}He did? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:39.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575221,579266}If you're okay with it, I'd like\Nto talk to you a little more about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579266,580935}What should we do, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582728,583813}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583813,584522}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585356,586524}What is it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586941,589068}Have you seen the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:52.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589068,592530}I bought the evening issue at Jones\Nwhen I was going back from work…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593405,595533}I wonder where I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596992,598994}Geez, Dad. It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:09:59.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598994,599870}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599870,601372}I left it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:06.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601372,606544}Here. I know how you always like to read\Nthe paper after a rough day at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606544,607419}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:09.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608546,609421}What is it, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611632,614051}Dad… Take a look at this…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614051,615719}This is… us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615719,616637}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:20.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617346,620015}Oh, it's John and Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:24.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620391,624270}A dog called Lassie walked\Nover six hundred miles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624270,627314}to reunite with her owner,\Na young boy named John.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:28.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627982,628774}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630067,633988}You've got your names\Nall over Britain!
Comment: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:36.82,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:636824,636824}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668314,670191}All of these for Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670191,671025}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:17.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671025,677114}People all over Britain read that article\Nand wrote fan letters to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:22.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677364,682912}It was the first time I've delivered\Nso many mails in a single minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:23.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682912,683871}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683871,684872}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684872,686832}Dad, you're awfully early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687708,689585}Ah, I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689585,691754}Well, I kind of ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692004,693130}Ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693130,694048}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:39.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694048,699762}You wouldn't believe how many journalists\Nare at the mine, hungry for an interview now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699970,701388}About Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701388,704642}I always knew this dog's future\Nwas different from other dogs'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704642,707645}Oh? So you mean she did\Nother unusual feats before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707645,709438}Yeah. Let me think…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:53.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709438,713275}When Dr. Hopper had fallen from the cliff,\Nshe was the one who saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713275,715110}Ah, can you tell us\Nmore about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715110,716320}Hey! Beal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716320,717988}Stop slacking, or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717988,720532}I'm not slacking, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721200,722868}So you're the boss here, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722868,724536}– Uh…\N– We'd like to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725913,727581}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727581,729250}Even in your clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729250,730960}So they're in the mine, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730960,732002}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732002,735839}We couldn't even examine\Nthe patients properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736215,737925}They're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:22.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737925,742304}Dr. Hopper had to go maximum\Ngrumpy on them before they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743555,745057}How John is doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:28.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745057,748185}He's gone with Priscilla\Nand the others to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748185,749228}He took Lassie with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749228,750104}Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751647,754108}How does it feel, John?\NYou're in all the newspapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754108,756277}You've become famous, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756527,758696}I haven't. Lassie has!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:42.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759238,762533}We're so far away from the town\Nthat no one should follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762533,763784}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765619,766578}The Rocky Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:51.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767329,771583}Lassie is in good health. How about\Nwe go all the way to the top again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:52.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771583,772459}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779383,781051}Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781427,783012}Mr. McNeill…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783846,785014}How did you know about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:09.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785014,789018}I'm a journalist.\NI can connect a few dots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:14.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789810,794023}In fact, I wanted to invite\NJohn and Lassie to a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:14.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794356,794940}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794940,796400}A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:22.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797526,802406}So this is your secret base,\Nright inside this rock formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802948,804575}Can you climb to the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804575,807578}Perfect. Could you pretend\Nyou're climbing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807578,808912}I'll take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808912,810205}No, we've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810205,811665}We're busy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811665,813625}Right. What do you have there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813625,816712}They're messages to Lassie\Nfrom people who read the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816712,819798}I have to read them\Nfor Lassie and reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820841,822301}– Let's see.\N– Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:46.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822926,826180}It's very rude to read\Nsomeone's private letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826180,828682}Y-You're right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829183,831185}He's not one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831185,833562}How long is he gonna stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833562,834146}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834146,835439}– Ah!\N– What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835689,837358}This letter…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837358,839193}Ah, wait a moment, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839943,842905}Right, you must\Nrecognize the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:04.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843822,844698}What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:08.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845074,848869}It's a letter from someone\Nwho Lassie met on her journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850913,852790}{\i1}To my dear Purcell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:16.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852790,856377}{\i1}No, your name is\Nactually Lassie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856835,859797}{\i1}Dan went out to the village\Nto sell the eggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859797,862758}{\i1}and he came back holding\Na newspaper with your picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:28.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863592,868722}{\i1}As we thought, you already had a family\Nand you wanted to come back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:33.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869056,873727}{\i1}We didn't make a mistake\Nwhen we sent you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:37.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873727,877189}{\i1}You must be happy to have\Nreturned to your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877189,879274}{\i1}We are also very happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879274,882694}"We send our greetings\Nto your precious family".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882694,884196}It's a wonderful letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:44.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884196,884738}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884738,886365}They're kind people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:50.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886365,890244}Lassie, you have met\Nmany people on your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890244,893831}I'd like to meet and thank\Nthese people one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:59.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894748,899169}So what do you think? Aren't you\Nhappy that we published your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899169,900587}Yes… I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900587,902923}So, about that party…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902923,904341}Yes. What's the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904633,907719}Duke Radling said\Nhe would like to have a party
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:11.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907719,911390}for a great dog Lassie,\Nwho finished a journey like no other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912015,914852}He also wants to apologize\Nto the people from your town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915102,916228}Grandfather…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:19.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916478,919231}So I thought of a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:22.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919231,922234}Why not invite\Nthe two of you to this party?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922693,923777}How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:27.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924445,927865}I'm sure you guys will\Ngladly attend the party, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931201,933370}Ah, one more thing\Nabout the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933370,936957}I've got a small favor to ask, could you\Nkeep it a secret from the other papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936957,938709}We hope for\Nan exclusive coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:43.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939418,943964}Pff. In the end,\Nwe didn't climb to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:47.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944339,947301}What a shame, today\Neven Priscilla was with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:07.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962816,967446}I've been dying to eat something all day.\NThat feast came just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967446,969990}All thanks to John and Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969990,971033}Damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:14.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971617,974620}Is everything ready, McNeil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974620,976038}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976747,979416}John and the miners are all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:25.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979416,985297}I am sure they will\Nappreciate your gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:30.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986089,990052}Well, I'll better go check\Non our main guest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:41.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993472,1001146}I kept silent and let that youngster\Nfrom the paper do as he pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001146,1004191}But if I had to decide for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:48.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004191,1008612}I wouldn't put this pressure\Non John, Lassie and the miners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008612,1011573}What was I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012741,1014785}Hey, now. We can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014785,1017704}Our main guest\Nis still dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:00.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017704,1020457}This boy just won't stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020457,1022834}Do I really have to wear these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022834,1024294}Just… Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025045,1026922}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:10.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026922,1030801}Duke Radling has invited\Nmany people from high society.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:13.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030801,1033512}You need to look the part,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033512,1037307}Do my usual clothes\Nlook that indecent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037891,1039560}That's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:23.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039560,1043689}You prevented an entire coal mine\Nfrom shutting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043689,1046650}You did what no adult could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046650,1049653}Duke Radling\Nadmires you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049653,1052364}This is why you should present\Nyourself in your finest form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:36.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052364,1056618}I'm just trying to help you,\Nthinking of your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056618,1057703}Did you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:42.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057703,1062416}If you do as I say, everyone will treat you\Nlike an adult from today on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:46.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062416,1066712}You see, you can't run in the field\Nin these clothes forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067462,1068672}All right, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068672,1071675}I'll take a stunning photo of you\Nwhen you make your entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:52.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071675,1072718}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072718,1074011}Oh! Mr. McNeill…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:55.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074386,1075137}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075137,1076013}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:18:00.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076263,1080892}Will Mr. Dan and Ms. Dally\Nreally come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081101,1082728}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:07.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082728,1087024}The elderly couple who helped Lassie find\Nher owner will be one of today's highlights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:10.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087024,1090277}They seem to be\Na little late, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090277,1091111}Ah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:11.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091111,1091653}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091903,1093405}What… What about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:16.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093614,1096033}Rest assured,\Nshe's not gonna go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096033,1097993}She's getting decorated\Nin the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097993,1099119}Decorated?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099119,1100329}You mean, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100329,1103332}Next, we have to do something\Nwith this hair of yours…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104291,1106084}Everything is going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106084,1107461}All right, just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:31.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107461,1111006}We've got to make it\Nmove other guests to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:31.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111006,1111798}Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111798,1113884}Tears sell well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:34.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113884,1114718}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115594,1117429}Oh, I'm glad to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:41.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117429,1121433}The pleasure is all mine. I'd love to have\Nsuch a great dog myself some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121433,1122100}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122100,1123602}I'll be damned, if it's not the Duke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123602,1125937}Lots of important people…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:49.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125937,1129024}Everyone read about Lassie\Nin the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129024,1131860}They look forward to\NJohn's future endeavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132986,1135530}All right, be a good dog\Nand wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135530,1138575}I couldn't do anything\Nabout her ear, so I put a bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138575,1140369}Isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141453,1143038}It seems to have started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143038,1145123}I'll call you when you're up,\Nso just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145624,1147959}What's with all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149628,1152964}Not that I'm one to talk…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155258,1157094}Say…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157094,1160889}Do you really think\Nwe look like adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162015,1163642}Something's way off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:28.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164518,1168063}I found new coal deposits\Nand you had a brush with death
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:31.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168063,1171066}just so that we could\Nlook like a pair of clowns?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171066,1173527}That's wrong.\NThat's not how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177322,1178365}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:44.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178365,1184246}the story of Lassie's long journey\Nwas full of misfortunes and fatigue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184246,1187791}It was all to reunite\Nwith her beloved owner, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:54.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187791,1194506}But John swore for the sake of his hometown\Nto find new coal deposits, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:20:00.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194506,1200137}"Lassie! I'm sorry, but I cannot go\Nlooking for you." Truly heartbreaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:05.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200595,1205642}His feelings to save Greenall Bridge\Ncrossed the great distance between them
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:09.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205642,1209104}and helped Lassie maintain the\Ndetermination to find her way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209104,1210564}Let me introduce to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:15.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210564,1215694}the amazing dog Lassie,\Nand its owner John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220782,1223493}What happened?\NNobody's showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225996,1227748}What happened to John?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:30.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228206,1230625}He left this message…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:34.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231585,1234129}Damn, they run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234963,1237132}{\i1}To Duke Radling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:41.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237132,1241136}{\i1}We are not in a hurry\Nto join the adult world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:47.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241553,1247517}{\i1}I just want to run around\Nin the fields together with Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247517,1249478}{\i1}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:53.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249853,1253231}I apologize to everyone\Nfor this confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253231,1255108}John Carraclough…
Comment: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:57.92,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1317921,1317921}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:03.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320674,1323260}{\i1}I'm Remi, and I sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323260,1325428}{\i1}Nope, I don't feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:08.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325428,1328139}{\i1}I have a lot of nice friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:10.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328139,1330725}{\i1}But where is my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331142,1332936}{\i1}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333979,1336606}{\i1}"Remi, Nobody's Girl".\NLook forward to it!
