Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:33.70,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1349911,1353707}and I run with you up the hill
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:36.91,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1354040,1356918}We can see the distant skies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:41.75,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1357752,1361756}I still remember that time, woo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:44.75,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1361965,1364759}Falling out of the pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:49.43,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1365760,1369431}a candy and the sands of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:52.55,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1369639,1372559}The journey has begun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:57.14,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1373101,1377147}to become an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:00.56,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1377647,1380567}The hot burning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:04.65,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1380984,1384654}setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:08.40,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1384863,1388408}is still high in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:12.49,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1388658,1392495}People and towns are waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:16.08,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1392704,1396082}You promised
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:20.00,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1396333,1400003}with a big smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.84,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1400253,1403840}after we crossed that hill
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:30.93,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1403965,1410931}that someday we'll fulfill our dreams
